{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"72b90139-77f2-4716-81f3-39822a40fda6","content":"## MSTest v3 `.testsettings` Migration\n\nMSTest v3 **no longer supports `.testsettings` files**. You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file and MSTest properties in the `.csproj`.\n\nHere's how to migrate your three configurations:\n\n### 1. Create a `.runsettings` file\n\nReplace `local.testsettings` with a `.runsettings` file:\n\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n        uri=\"datacollector://microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n        assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.CoverageCollectorDataCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral\" />\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <DeploymentEnabled>false</DeploymentEnabled>\n  </MSTest>\n</RunSettings>\n```\n\n### 2. Set the test timeout in `.csproj`\n\nAdd MSTest timeout configuration to your project:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\nOr use `[Timeout(30000)]` attributes on individual tests/classes.\n\n### 3. Wire the `.runsettings` in `.csproj`\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <RunSettingsFilePath>$(MSBuildProjectDirectory)\\.runsettings</RunSettingsFilePath>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n### Summary of changes\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | MSTest v3 equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout` property | `<TestTimeout>` in csproj or `[Timeout]` attribute |\n| Code Coverage DataCollector | `<DataCollectors>` in `.runsettings` |\n| Deployment/AssemblyResolution | `<DeploymentEnabled>` in `.runsettings` (deployment is off by default in v3) |\n\nAfter migrating, you can delete `local.testsettings`. Would you like me to apply these changes to your project?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"91a7f879-de82-429f-835d-0f55fdf2d07b","outputTokens":548,"requestId":"E3C3:2C57B5:ABC2AB:C4A20D:6A053A81"},"id":"143b3298-c9af-43a9-b8ab-1756bdc01f0a","timestamp":"2026-05-14T02:59:23.441Z","parentId":"7a0434cd-ed59-4508-88f0-99df2c14ac09"}
